lve apostles, referred to as ‘Thomas, called Didymus’ (John 11:16; 20:24). <i>Didymos</i> is the Greek word for ‘twin’, and the name is the Greek form of an Aramaic byname meaning ‘twin’. The given name has always been popular throughout Christendom, in part because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mom Phelps was born in 1500, in Midlothian, Scotland. She married Dad Phelps. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1500–":"1500–Surnud","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–Surnud","1567":"1567","1500":"1500","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","about 1522":"umbes 1522","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland"},"fi":{"1500–":"1500–Kuollut","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–Kuollut","1567":"1567","1500":"1500","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","about 1522":"noin 1522","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland"},"fr":{"1500–":"1500–Décédée","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–Décédée","1567":"1567","1500":"1500","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","about 1522":"environ 1522","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Mom Phelps est née en 1500, à Midlothian, Écosse. Elle a épousé Dad Phelps. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1500–":"1500–Verstorben","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–Verstorben","1567":"1567","1500":"1500","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","about 1522":"um 1522","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Mom Phelps wurde 1500 in Midlothian, Scotland geboren. Sie hat Dad Phelps geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1500–":"1500–Desede","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–Desede","1567":"1567","1500":"1500","1522":"1522","1620":"1620","about 1522":"about 1522","Midlothian, Scotland":"Midlothian, Scotland"},"hu":{"1500–":"1500–elhunyt","1500–1567":"1500–1567","1522–1620":"1522–1620","1500–Female":"1500–elhunyt